                     <interp inst="t18341205-274-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="simpleLarceny"></interp> for stealing, on the <rs id="t18341205-cd-68" type="crimeDate">
                        <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18341205-274-offence-1 t18341205-cd-68"></join>9th of December</rs>, 1 cloak, value 2<hi rend="italic">l</hi>. 10<hi rend="italic">s</hi>., the goods of <persName id="t18341205-name-518" type="victimName">
